videos.description: Justin Jenifer sets up Gary Clark under the hoops with a no-look pass to put the Bearcats up 35-21.
videos.headline: No-look pass lead to nice Bearcats bucket

videos.description: Gary Clark gets the rebound and takes it himself to the hole to increase Cincinnati's lead.
videos.headline: Clark takes it coast to coast for Bearcats

videos.description: Justin Jenifer gets fancy on the drive and draws the foul for Cincinnati.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's  Jenifer cuts to basket for hoop and harm
